<P>
Photo, COLOR, (Orange County Edition) San Diego State's Joe McNaull tries to 
keep the ball from Tracy Murray during UCLA's 94-74 victory Saturday at Pauley 
Pavilion. ROBERT DURELL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
