</P>
<P>
"I liked the simplicity of the basketball player and that it's a game. I think 
it's the only float that isn't coming out of this fantasy world. I think it was 
a gutsy move for ITT and Sheraton to have a black man dunking a basketball in a 
parade." 
</P>
<P>
