<P>
Photo, Sophomore Dionne Vanlandingham leads Cal State Dominguez Hills in 
scoring and rebounding. ; Photo, Vanlandingham, guarding Simon Fraser's 
Michelle Hendry, makes up for a lack of size with quickness. BRIAN VANDER BRUG 
/ Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
