Photo, COLOR, (COVER) Garth Brooks, left. ROBERT DURELL / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, COLOR, (COVER) Wynonna Judd J. Albert Diaz / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
COLOR, (COVER) Clint Black Anacleto Rapping / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
