<P>
40. There are 30 Time magazine covers featuring Richard M. Nixon hanging in the 
new presidential library in Yorba Linda. How many times, total, has Nixon 
appeared on the news magazine's cover? 
</P>
<P>
a. 30 
</P>
<P>
b. 54 
</P>
<P>
c. 66 
</P>
<P>
d. 75 
</P>
