<TEXT>
<P>
Thanks, NBC, for "The Dreamer of Oz: The L. Frank Baum Story" (Dec. 10). 
</P>
<P>
We felt this rich, moving, quality production was TV at its best-the caliber of 
a Hallmark Hall of Fame program. (John) Ritter's performance was excellent. My 
wife still has a lump in her throat. 
</P>
<P>
George J. Sweikis, Alta Loma 
